    def get_all_consultants(token, page=1):
    consultants = []
    while True:
        response = requests.get(f'/api/v1/consultants?page={page}',
                              headers={'Authorization': f'Bearer {token}'})
        data = response.json()
        consultants.extend(data['data'])

        if page >= data['pagination']['pages']:
            break
        page += 1

    return consultants
